Tags:		display screen color temperature redshift
Comments:	----------
		Syntax: $ sct <color_temperature_in_K>
		Usage example: $ sct 4500
		Notes: 
		   - Color temperature must be between 1000 and 10000 and a multiple of 500
		   - Works for Xorg but not for Xfbdev
